svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104sqy1665702665979.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sqy1665702665979.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/sqy1665702665979.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"sqy1665702665979\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"sqy1665702665979___check_253750\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return or set the checked status of a menu item.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__topic_d80792e1_d80793e1_d80794e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80795e1_d80796e1_d80797e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80798e1_d80799e1_d80800e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80801e1_d80802e1_d80803e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__topic_d53212e1_d53213e1_d53214e1_d53215e1_d53216e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d501362e89\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__2\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__1\">1</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__2\">Menu item is checked.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__1\">0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"sqy1665702665979__table_d8048e1_d8049e1_d8050e1__entry__2\">Menu item is not checked.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80807e1_d80808e1_d80809e1\">In an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__topic_d53217e1_d53218e1_d53219e1_d53220e1_d53221e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d501362e144\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__d6620e20\">Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__topic_d53222e1_d53223e1_d53224e1_d53225e1_d53226e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d501362e153\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80819e1_d80820e1_d80821e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span> function determines whether a check mark appears next to the current menu item. The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span> does not affect the menu accelerator for that menu item.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"sqy1665702665979__p_d80822e1_d80823e1_d80824e1\">Since <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span> is a Boolean function, when <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var> evaluates to a non-zero value, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span> becomes 1.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukk1665702596834.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reset</a><p>Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>set</a><p>Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/air1665702666109.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$disable</a><p>Disables a menu item in a menu object.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sed1665702666179.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hide</a><p>Return or set the display status of a menu item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger preDisplay</a><p>System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532125\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532125\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$check Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return or set the checked status of a menu item. $check $check = Expression set | reset $check Return Values Value Meaning 1 Menu item is checked. 0 Menu item is not checked. In an error occurs, $procerror contains the exact error. Use Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects. Description The $check function determines whether a check mark appears next to the current menu item. The value of $check does not affect the menu accelerator for that menu item. Since $check is a Boolean function, when Expression evaluates to a non-zero value, $check becomes 1. Related Links reset Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0. set Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE). $disable Disables a menu item in a menu object. $hide Return or set the display status of a menu item. trigger preDisplay System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}